{"tid":1381013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廣告界嘅朋友 係時候到我地擺工!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T09:42:26.000Z","uid":143680,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9e5e324d20b2c3ed4a533a0bf9e58367a7b68c","tid":1381013,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:54:40.000Z","msg":"之前個post推極都唔起<br />\n<br />\n廣告界作為傳訊界樞紐，絕對不是獨善其身，吉野家事件可見一斑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n始於入行，一直以為品牌說故事作己任，如果你自己人生或「香港」是一個品牌呢？<br />\n而我會選擇用「廣告界從業員」身份，為社會發聲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有廣告人發起「廣告人表態行動」，希望同業可以<span style=\"color: red;\">一齊喺8月5日罷工一日</span>，以及當日午飯時間著黑衫到太古坊公眾位置表態。本版響應轉載如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">訴求如下</span></span><br />\n1. 政府立刻正名撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 立刻成立以大法官為首的獨立調查委員會作全面調查<br />\n3. 特首、律政司、保安局局長、警務處處長失職導致社會撕裂應問責下台<br />\n4. 停止白色恐佈，釋放所有政治犯，承諾不秋後算帳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建議行動如下：</span></span><br />\n1. 響應大三罷8月5日星期一罷工一天<br />\n2. 8月5日星期一於太古坊公眾位置自携午餐聯誼<br />\n3. 聯誼即場募捐登記，目標籌得$40,000登報章全版聯署聲明，餘款撥捐立場新聞<br />\n4. Dress code: Black<br />\n<br />\n#廣告人表態行動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/653481138013826/posts/2789644957730756?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F653481138013826%2Fposts%2F2789644957730756%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=80724224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/653481138013826/posts/2789644957730756?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QCELqO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9QCELqO.png&h=8abed992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推俾更多人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf4ec7d4cf10a6a83192d2a846348157b264f2c","tid":1381013,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"8月5號我要擺工!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"278d84f6658ff112df3b081ffb834c8bf1b01fe2","tid":1381013,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"8月5號我要擺工!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"e004ebe9603f47e43d68438fe4f816ae0a4231e7","tid":1381013,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:56:21.000Z","msg":"8月5號我要擺工!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"5210c78d980ee4349f77590f20ec25754b57b9a9","tid":1381013,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:56:31.000Z","msg":"8月5號我要擺工!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"73a42a4c33b33824aa39f14903e51f043f79290d","tid":1381013,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:56:55.000Z","msg":"8月5號我要擺工!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"34e275a34d00299b5166b84ce47d893edeaa83fd","tid":1381013,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:57:05.000Z","msg":"8月5號我要擺工!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"154801ede07eca17b777ff7a34f45cf5b51e9140","tid":1381013,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime